(26, 32, 61, 'new', 'probonocorpo_emailing', '{\r\n    "isc": {\r\n        "labels": {\r\n            "default": "The internal collaboration = an opportunity for your startup !",\r\n            "fr_FR": "La collaboration interne = une opportunit\\u00e9 pour ta startup !"\r\n        },\r\n        "cci": "probonocorpo.par@socgen.com",\r\n        "from_mail": "probonocorpo.par@socgen.com",\r\n        "from_name": "Pro Bono Corpo",\r\n        "subject": {\r\n            "default": "The internal collaboration = an opportunity for your startup !",\r\n            "fr_FR": "La collaboration interne = une opportunit\\u00e9 pour ta startup !"\r\n        },\r\n        "customizable": false,\r\n        "text": {\r\n            "default": "\\n<br \\/>Hello %s,\\n<br \\/>\\n<br \\/>You are an <strong>intrapreneur<\\/strong> and you have the ambition to develop an internal startup.\\n<br \\/>\\n<br \\/>Congratulations on accepting the challenge you are taking up with your team, given your limited means!\\n<br \\/>\\n<br \\/>The good news are you are not alone and <strong>you can rely on volontary contributors<\\/strong> who are there to help you!\\n<br \\/>\\n<br \\/><strong>ProBonoCorpo<\\/strong> allows you to find the right skills at the right time by connecting you with SG employees who can give you a hand.\\n<br \\/>\\n<br \\/>You just have to <strong>specify your one-time assistance needs<\\/strong> and also to let us know what skills you would be exchanging with your intrapreneur colleagues.\\n<br \\/>\\n<br \\/>In order to help us to launch our service soon, we invite you to clarify if you are rather a:\\n<br \\/><a href=\\"http:\\/\\/www.probonocorpo.com\\/landing\\/template2\\/probonocorpo\\/%s?hash=%s&property_1_contributor=contributor#survey\\"><img src=\\"http:\\/\\/img.p-pit.fr\\/select.png\\" width=\\"20\\" \\/><\\/a>&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>Contributor<\\/strong>\\n<br \\/><a href=\\"http:\\/\\/www.probonocorpo.com\\/landing\\/template2\\/probonocorpo\\/%s?hash=%s&property_1_requestor=requestor#survey\\"><img src=\\"http:\\/\\/img.p-pit.fr\\/select.png\\" width=\\"20\\" \\/><\\/a>&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>Requestor<\\/strong>\\n<br \\/><a href=\\"http:\\/\\/www.probonocorpo.com\\/landing\\/template2\\/probonocorpo\\/%s?hash=%s&property_1_contributor=contributor&property_1_requestor=requestor#survey\\"><img src=\\"http:\\/\\/img.p-pit.fr\\/select.png\\" width=\\"20\\" \\/><\\/a>&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>Contributor & requestor<\\/strong>\\n<br \\/><a href=\\"http:\\/\\/www.probonocorpo.com\\/landing\\/template2\\/probonocorpo\\/%s?hash=%s#survey\\"><img src=\\"http:\\/\\/img.p-pit.fr\\/select.png\\" width=\\"20\\" \\/><\\/a>&nbsp;&nbsp;You don\'t know yet\\n<br \\/>\\n<br \\/>We thank you for your contribution!\\n",\r\n            "fr_FR": "\\n<br \\/>Bonjour %s,\\n<br \\/>\\n<br \\/>Tu es <strong>intrapreneur<\\/strong> et tu as l\'ambition de d&eacute;velopper une startup interne.\\n<br \\/>\\n<br \\/>Bravo pour le d&eacute;fi que tu rel&egrave;ves avec ton &eacute;quipe et des moyens limit&eacute;s !\\n<br \\/>\\n<br \\/>La bonne nouvelle, c\\u2019est que vous n\\u2019&ecirc;tes pas seuls et que <strong>vous pouvez compter sur des contributeurs volontaires<\\/strong> pour vous aider !\\n<br \\/>\\n<br \\/><strong>ProBonoCorpo<\\/strong> vous permet de trouver les bonnes comp&eacute;tences au bon moment en vous mettant en contact avec les collaborateurs SG disponibles pour un coup de main.\\n<br \\/>\\n<br \\/>Il suffit de <strong>pr&eacute;ciser tes besoins d\'assistance ponctuelle<\\/strong> et aussi de proposer les comp&eacute;tences que tu pourrais &eacute;changer avec tes coll&egrave;gues intrapreneurs.\\n<br \\/>\\n<br \\/>Pour nous aider &agrave; lancer rapidement notre service, nous t\'invitons &agrave; pr&eacute;ciser si tu es plut&ocirc;t :\\n<br \\/><a href=\\"http:\\/\\/www.probonocorpo.com\\/landing\\/template2\\/probonocorpo\\/%s?hash=%s&property_1_contributor=contributor#survey\\"><img src=\\"http:\\/\\/img.p-pit.fr\\/select.p